These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: lemon, broccoli
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, traveling
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, pop
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
6. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the fan of pop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | lemonade |
| Food          | broccoli      | lemon       |
| Hobby         | traveling | board-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | thriller      |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | pop      |
| Sport         | surfing    | tennis       |

