.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, cherry
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, librarian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, rock
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the bartender is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the bartender is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
6. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food          | eggplant | cherry |
| Hobby         | reading  | singing  |
| Job           | bartender      | librarian  |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | house      |
| Pet           | bird     | fish    |
| Transport     | airplane  | bike     |

