2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
4. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |
