3. the fan of metal is the person drinking water##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
5. the firefighter is on the left of the fan of metal##1
6. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person drinking water##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |         2          |
| Beverage      | 7up          | water               |
| Food          | zucchini       | lime           |
| Hobby         | photography       | card-games            |
| Job           | firefighter | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | metal            |
| Transport     | train   | airplane               |

 